%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20I%20try%20to%20go%20outside.%20It%20makes%20a%20huge%20difference%20in%20helping%20me%20gain%20perspective%20on%20whatever%20issues%20I%20have.%20The%20magnitude%20of%20nature%20helps%20me%20see%20that%20I'm%20putting%20energy%20into%20something%20that%20actually%20doesn't%20matter%20that%20much.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222cd22ed5-8da4-42c5-aaa6-2204a096281c%5C%22%3EI%20get%20on%20a%20yoga%20mat%20almost%20every%20day%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20I%20get%20on%20my%20yoga%20mat%2C%20I%20often%20scan%20my%20email%20for%2030%20to%2045%20minutes.%20I%20generally%20have%20something%20that%20I%20know%20has%20to%20get%20done%2C%20and%20I%20try%20to%20do%20that%20first%20thing%20so%20it's%20not%20hanging%20over%20my%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20I%20get%20to%20my%20yoga%20practice.%20I%20have%20a%20yoga%20teacher%2C%20who%20I've%20been%20working%20with%20for%2015%20years.%20So%2C%20I'll%20either%20get%20on%20my%20mat%20at%20home%20and%20practice%20with%20her%2C%20or%20I'll%20go%20to%20a%20CorePower%20studio%20or%20tune%20in%20to%20a%20livestream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228110%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Niki%20Leondakis%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69163ec2e1a9cbb014de2c5d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%226083%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELeondakis%20tries%20to%20get%20on%20a%20yoga%20mat%20every%20day%2C%20even%20if%20it's%20just%20for%2015%20minutes.%3Cp%3EMatthew%20DeFeo%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20on%20the%20busiest%20days%2C%20I%20have%20what%20I%20call%20my%20minimum%20required%20practice%2C%20or%20MRP.%20Even%20if%20it's%20just%2015%20minutes%2C%20I%20try%20to%20do%20sun%20salutations%2C%20breath%20work%2C%20and%20ground%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20eat%20in%20the%20morning%20until%20I'm%20hungry.%20But%20if%20I%20had%20a%20really%20vigorous%20practice%2C%20I'll%20have%20Greek%20yogurt%20with%20chia%20seeds%2C%20fresh%20berries%2C%20and%20some%20low-sugar%20type%20of%20granola.%20Usually%20at%20that%20time%2C%20I'll%20have%20a%20second%20cup%20of%20my%20mushroom%20tea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22db16e8cc-2add-4d8e-947d-2594eada80cc%5C%22%3EI'm%20online%20by%208%3A30%20a.m.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20first%20calls%20are%20around%208%3A30%20or%209%20a.m.%2C%20and%20I%20have%20them%20on%20Zoom%20or%20in%20our%20headquarters%20boardroom.%20I%20typically%20visit%20studios%20or%20meet%20with%20managers%20and%20leaders.%20Sometimes%2C%20I'll%20do%20a%20listening%20tour%20with%20our%20yoga%20teachers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22282ce295-aadc-481c-91f0-810b16664802%5C%22%3EAs%20an%20introvert%2C%20my%20days%20are%20scheduled%20very%20specifically%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20me%20to%20be%20my%20best%20self%2C%20I%20cannot%20be%20in%20back-to-back%20meetings.%20I%20need%20time%20to%20process%2C%20or%20maybe%20send%20a%20follow-up%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20have%20big%20presentations%20or%20something%20high-stakes%2C%20my%20assistant%20knows%20to%20schedule%2030%20minutes%20before%20the%20meeting%20so%20I%20can%20ground%20myself%20and%20do%20breath%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227871%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Niki%20Leondakis%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69163ef8abd5e944effab2cd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225903%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELeondakis%20said%20she%20needs%20time%20to%20recharge%20after%20meetings.%3Cp%3EMatthew%20DeFeo%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20introverted.%20I%20think%20of%20my%20body%2C%20mind%2C%20and%20spirit%20as%20an%20iPhone.%20My%20battery%20charges%20up%20in%20my%20alone%20time%2C%20whether%20that's%20getting%20outside%2C%20spending%20time%20in%20nature%2C%20practicing%20meditation%2C%20engaging%20in%20breath%20work%2C%20or%20reading.%20I%20find%20it%20enjoyable%20to%20interact%20in%20a%20big%20social%20environment%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F