m%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20a%20director%20at%20a%20Series%20A%20health%20tech%20SaaS%20platform%2C%20managing%20a%20team%20and%20the%20strategy%20for%20a%20global%20clinician%20network.%20I%20worked%20at%20the%20startup%20for%20just%20under%20two%20years%2C%20moving%20to%20a%20different%20role%20during%20one%20reorg%2C%20and%20then%20later%20getting%20laid%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20my%20first%20layoff%2C%20but%20I'd%20been%20out%20of%20work%20before%2C%20and%20I%20wasn't%20new%20to%20the%20shame%20of%20not%20having%20a%20job%20and%20trying%20to%20figure%20out%20my%20identity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20nothing%20prepared%20me%20for%20what%20I%20encountered%20after%20this%20layoff%3A%20Nearly%20two%20years%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftwo-years-2000-applications-how-got-job-offer-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejob%20searching%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20passed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20I'm%20no%20longer%20actively%20looking%20for%20a%20new%20position.%20The%20idea%20of%20going%20out%20on%20my%20own%20was%20always%20in%20the%20back%20of%20my%20mind%2C%20but%20it%20was%20never%20something%20I%20had%20executed%20on%20%E2%80%94%20until%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225bfba013-a8a3-4477-b17b-f27900804678%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20was%20pretty%20disappointed%20to%20be%20laid%20off%2C%20and%20shame%20set%20in%20pretty%20quickly%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20prided%20myself%20on%20my%20career%20success%2C%20so%20there%20was%20this%20extreme%20loss%20of%20identity%20and%20purpose.%20My%20son%20was%20nine%20months%20old%2C%20and%20I%20felt%20like%20I'd%20let%20my%20husband%20and%20son%20down.%20I%20felt%20stunned%20and%20defeated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20already%20been%20feeling%20conflicted%20because%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworking-mom-leadership-transformation-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebecoming%20a%20mom%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20also%20a%20complete%20loss%20of%20identi