folio%20managers%20in%202024%20%E2%80%94%20roughly%20three%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e4a3093c-9a18-4c81-8e04-75816b3ec078%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20will%20fill%20Izzy's%20shoes%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEnglander%2C%20by%20all%20accounts%2C%20is%20not%20expected%20to%20go%20anywhere%20anytime%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%2077-year-old%20billionaire%20has%20built%20up%20his%20bench%20with%20plenty%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoldman-sachs-alumni-being-hired-by-top-hedge-funds-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eformer%20Goldman%20Sachs%20executives%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20he's%20ready%20to%20step%20down.%20All%20four%20members%20of%20his%20office%20of%20the%20CIO%20%E2%80%94%20Justin%20Gmelich%2C%20Scott%20Rofey%2C%20Paul%20Russo%2C%20and%20Jeff%20Verschleiser%20%E2%80%94%20were%20partners%20at%20the%20revered%20investment%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnglander's%20right-hand%20man%2C%20former%20Barclays%20and%20Lehman%20Brothers%20executive%20Ajay%20Nagpal%2C%20added%20President%20to%20his%20title%20alongside%20COO%20in%20late%202022%2C%20when%20the%20office%20of%20the%20CIO%20was%20also%20created.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAny%20new%20investor%20or%20partner%20in%20the%20firm%20who%20is%20concerned%20about%20Millennium%20changing%20drastically%20when%20Englander%20eventually%20departs%20shouldn't%20worry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20billionaire%20wrote%20in%202023%20to%20investors%2C%20the%20management%20structure%20helming%20the%20ship%20looks%20after%20%26quot%3Bthe%20wider%20interests%20of%20the%20organization%20and%2C%20crucially%2C%20the%20interests%20of%20you%2C%20our%20investors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20of%20these%20management%20layers%20as%20extensions%20of%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennium-izzy-englander-hedge-fund-future-stake-sale-2025-11%5C%22%3