20likely%20lower%20it%20by%20comparing%20rates%20to%20a%20competitor%20company%2C%20but%20I've%20been%20pushing%20off%20that%20phone%20call%20because%20I'm%20exhausted%20from%20dealing%20with%20automated%20systems%2C%20long%20call%20wait%20times%2C%20and%20automated%20voices%20that%20can't%20decipher%20what%20I'm%20saying%20when%20I%20beg%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcustomer-service-phone-calls-paid-status-symbol-luxury-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espeak%20with%20a%20human%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20seemed%20more%20work%20than%20it%20was%20worth.%20But%20what%20if%20I%20could%20outsource%20this%20chore%2C%20for%20free%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20a%20generative%20AI%20voice%20tool%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20turn%20myself%20into%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-satya-nadella-software-pricing-ai-agent-copilot2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eagent%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Agentic%20me%20was%20tasked%20with%20trying%20to%20get%20my%20internet%20price%20lowered%20and%20programmed%20it%20to%20be%20short%20on%20patience%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20bossy%20tone%20that%20made%20me%20cringe%20and%20feel%20sympathy%20for%20the%20human%20worker%20on%20the%20other%20side.%20Agentic%20me%20often%20restated%20some%20version%20of%20what%20the%20customer%20service%20rep%20told%20it%2C%20then%20said%20it%20was%20disappointed%2C%20and%20started%20hallucinating%20lower%20rates%20offered%20by%20competitor%20companies%20to%20compare%20prices.%20%26quot%3BI've%20been%20a%20loyal%20customer%20for%20a%20while%20now%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20it's%20fair%20that%20new%20customers%20get%20better%20deals%2C%26quot%3B%20my%20agent%20snapped.%20%26quot%3BIt%20sounds%20like%20you're%20telling%20me%20I%20should%20just%20go%20ahead%20and%20cancel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-bubble-boom-goldman-sachs-crash-risk-forecast-outlook-valuation-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20boom%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20just%20as%20customers%20are%20straining%20to%20get%20human%20representatives%20on%20the%20line%2C%20human%20representatives%20are%20now%20straining%20to%20decipher%20if%20they're%20talking%20to%20human%20customers.%20Call%20center%20workers%20are%20up%20against%20convincing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerica-small-business-owners-swamped-by-scammers-generative-ai-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeepfake%3C%2Fa%3E%20tech%20as%20the%20realistic%20distance%20between%20human%20and%20agentic%20callers%20narrows.%20As%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-tech-bubble-consumer-impact-business-adoption-goldman-sachs-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20tools%20for%20consumers%3C%2Fa%3E%20become%20widely%20available%2C%20there's%20also%20opportunities%20for%20people%20to%20use%20them%20not%20just%20for%20malicious%20fraud%2C%20but%20to%20troll%20call%20centers%20by%20sending%20agents%20to%20attack%20them%20en%20masse%20and%20waste%20time.%20Or%2C%20as%20in%20my%20case%2C%20as%20a%20regular%2C%20frazzled%20customer%20turning%20to%20them%20to%20make%20calls%20on%20their%20behalf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20in%20the%20early%20days%20of%20a%20large%20emerging%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Brian%20Levin%2C%20chief%20customer%20officer%20at%20Reality%20Defender%2C%20which%20makes%20software%20for%20governments%2C%20financial%20institutions%2C%20and%20other%20businesses%20to%20detect%20the%20likelihood%20that%20content%20was%20generated%20by%20AI%20in%20real%20time%20(Reality%20Defender%20helped%20me%20navigate%20the%20process%20of%20making%20myself%20an%20agent%20for%20this%20story).%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAnd%20the%20development%20of%20agentic%20callers%20%26quot%3Bis%20moving%20much%20faster%20than%20these%20contact%20centers%20typically%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAcross%20industries%2C%20there's%20a%20surge%20in%20AI%20voice%20agents%20targeting%20customer%20support%20service%20lines%2C%20driving%20new%20forms%20of%20fraud%20while%20dramatically%20increasing%20call%20volumes%20and%20operational%20strain%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Emily%20Fontaine%2C%20global%20head%20of%20venture%20capital%20at%20IBM%2C%20a%20partner%20and%20investor%20in%20Reality%20Defender%2C%20tells%20me%20in%20an%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatrick%20Carroll%2C%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20deepfake%20detector%20ValidSoft%2C%20tells%20me%20in%20an%20email%20that%20call%20centers%20are%20increasingly%20fielding%20calls%20from%20agents%20that%20attempt%20to%20thwart%20security%20protocols%20and%20authentication%20methods.%20%26quot%3BEven%20companies%20with%20strong%20defences%20are%20seeing%20rising%20call%20volumes%20as%20voice%20automation%20tools%20become%20more%20accessible%20and%20sophisticated%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20is%20a%20catch-22%20for%20customer%20service.%20A%20report%20released%20earlier%20this%20year%20by%20the%20IT%20research%20firm%20Gartner%20predicts%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fandrej-karpathy-ai-agents-timelines-openai-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20agents%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20resolve%2080%25%20of%20common%20issues%20for%20customers%20by%202029%2C%20potentially%20cutting%20operating%20costs%20by%2030%25.%20Another%20Gartner%20survey%20of%20customer%20support%20leaders%20found%20that%2085%25%20of%20them%20are%20interested%20in%20or%20using%20AI%20chatbots%2C%20but%20only%2011%25%20report%20that%20the%20investment%20so%20far%20has%20%26quot%3Bmostly%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bfully%26quot%3B%20met%20expectations.%20As%20they%20try%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20automation%20in%20customer%20service%20works%20best%2C%20fraudsters%20and%20callers%20who%20want%20to%20use%20agents%20themselves%20could%20upend%20the%20model%2C%20and%20trigger%20an%20AI%20vs.%20AI%20arms%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20easier%20it%20becomes%20to%20have%20a%20no-nonsense%2C%20hardline%20negotiating%20AI%20version%20of%20you%20call%20up%20your%20cable%20provider%2C%20your%20dentist%2C%20or%20Williams%20Sonoma%2C%20the%20number%20of%20customers%20creating%20AI%20versions%20of%20themselves%20will%20multiply.%20Daniel%20O'Sullivan%2C%20a%20senior%20director%20analyst%20at%20Gartner%2C%20tells%20me%20that%20%26quot%3Bcustomers%20want%20to%20outsource%20these%20types%20of%20requests%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20companies%20will%20eventually%20%26quot%3Bhave%20to%20get%20with%20the%20program.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20O'Sullivan%20adds%2C%20allowing%20agentic%20callers%20poses%20risks%20for%20companies%3A%20They%20need%20to%20find%20ways%20to%20evaluate%20calls%20for%20fraud%2C%20may%20receive%20more%20calls%20seeking%20service%20as%20the%20lift%20to%20deal%20with%20minor%20billing%20or%20service%20problems%20lowers%2C%20and%20they%20could%20lose%20out%20on%20building%20relationships%20with%20customers%2C%20something%20that%20human%20agents%20do%20when%20they%20go%20above%20and%20beyond%20for%20callers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAttempts%20to%20thwart%20call%20waiting%20aren't%20new.%20About%20half%20of%20customers%20say%20they%20try%20third-party%20channels%2C%20like%20Google%2C%20Reddit%2C%20or%20ChatGPT%2C%20to%20try%20to%20resolve%20a%20service%20issue%20before%20they%20even%20bother%20contacting%20the%20company%2C%20according%20to%20another%202025%20survey%20from%20Gartner.%20In%202010%2C%20a%20startup%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F5-time-saving-apps-for-the-busy-small-business-owner-2012-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELucyPhone%3C%2Fa%3E%20tried%20to%20best%20call%20waiting.%20It%20allowed%20people%20to%20hang%20up%20on%20customer%20service%2C%20and%20then%20receive%20a%20call%20back%20when%20it%20was%20their%20turn%20in%20line.%20The%20Reserve%20with%20Google%20tool%20can%20book%20restaurant%20reservations%20on%20your%20behalf.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frobot-lawyer-ai-donotpay-sued-practicing-law-without-a-license-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDoNotPay%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20startup%20that%20uses%20AI%20to%20help%20people%20fight%20fees%2C%20tickets%2C%20and%20search%20for%20money%20users%20may%20be%20owed%2C%20has%20gained%20attention%20for%20successfully%20acting%20as%20an%20advocate%20for%20individuals%20against%20big%20corporations%20that%20often%20have%20roadblocks%20to%20contact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESetting%20the%20agent%20up%20to%20do%20my%20bidding%20took%20some%20finessing%2C%20and%20about%20an%20hour's%20worth%20of%20work%20to%20clone%20my%20voice%20from%20audio%20in%20a%20radio%20interview%20I%20did%2C%20and%20then%20program%20the%20necessary%20info%20for%20my%20account%2C%20so%20my%20agent%20knew%20it%20like%20the%20back%20of%20its%20cold%2C%20coded%20hand.%20It%20wasn't%20a%20time%20saver%2C%20but%20this%20voice%20generating%20tech%20has%20become%20remarkably%20more%20sophisticated%20and%20simpler%20than%20when%20I%20tried%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbank-account-scam-deepfakes-ai-voice-generator-crime-fraud-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esimilar%20experiment%20with%20my%20bank%3C%2Fa%3E%20just%20six%20months%20ago.%20Back%20then%2C%20I%20had%20to%20painstakingly%20generate%20each%20sentence%20and%20all%20of%20the%20information%20I%20might%20need%2C%20anticipating%20the%20questions%20I%20would%20be%20asked%20by%20the%20representative%20before%20getting%20on%20the%20call.%20I%20had%20to%20save%20them%20as%20audio%20files%2C%20and%20then%20hit%20play%20on%20each%20quickly%20when%20asked.%20But%20programming%20this%20conversational%20agent%20was%20more%20like%20creating%20a%20character%20with%20a%20few%20boundaries%20and%20setting%20it%20loose%20to%20chat%20in%20real-time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20entirely%20feasible%20for%20somebody%20to%20do%20that%20just%20as%20a%20hobby%20project%20just%20to%20really%20make%20a%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Matt%20Smallman%2C%20a%20call%20center%20security%20expert.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20a%20bit%20nervous%20about%20what%20the%20future%20does%20hold%2C%26quot%3B%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20calling%2C%20he%20says.%20It's%20easy%20to%20imagine%20a%20world%20in%20which%20these%20tools%20become%20so%20easy%20to%20use%2C%20more%20people%20would%20take%20them%20up%20%E2%80%94%20both%20to%20troll%20call%20centers%2C%20and%20to%20handle%20the%20mundane%20and%20tedious%20tasks%20of%20contacting%20help%20lines%20for%20banks%2C%20healthcare%20systems%2C%20and%20retail%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgent%20me%20was%20not%20able%20to%20convince%20the%20call%20center%20worker%20that%20I%20deserved%20to%20have%20my%20bill%20lowered%20back%20to%20the%20promotional%20rate%20(the%20customer%20service%20rep%20told%20me%20that%20the%20company%20doesn't%20match%20competitor%20prices%2C%20and%20once%20my%20introductory%20rate%20came%20to%20a%20close%2C%20there%20wasn't%20a%20better%20offer%20to%20give%20me).%20But%20it%20did%20try%20to%20keep%20the%20representative%20on%20the%20line%2C%20who%20showed%20no%20signs%20of%20suspicion%20that%20they%20were%20speaking%20to%20an%20agent.%20In%20a%20five-minute-long%2C%20sometimes%20tense%20back-and-forth%2C%20my%20agent%20repeatedly%20threatened%20to%20cancel%20service%20and%20said%20the%20rates%20offered%20just%20weren't%20good%20enough%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bloyal%20customer%26quot%3B%20like%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20agent%20exhausted%20all%20options%2C%20it%20asked%20to%20be%20transferred%20to%20someone%20who%20could%20get%20the%20job%20done.%20I%20quickly%20cut%20it%20off%2C%20fearful%20that%20the%20agent%20might%20be%20too%20effective%20in%20canceling%20my%20much-needed%20wifi.%20The%20agent%20had%20a%20singular%20goal%2C%20and%20was%20willing%20to%20stay%20on%20the%20phone%20indefinitely%20to%20achieve%20it.%20Given%20the%20nuance%20of%20the%20situation%2C%20I'm%20not%20ready%20to%20unleash%20an%20agent%20to%20do%20my%20bidding%20%E2%80%94%20I'd%20rather%20call%20for%20myself%20and%20ask%20nicely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Famanda-hoover%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EAmanda%20Hoover%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%20covering%20the%20tech%20industry.%20She%20writes%20about%20the%20biggest%20tech%20companies%20and%20trends.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscammed-internet-provider-lower-my-bill-deepfakes-ai-2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1763370661000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6917743de1a9cbb014de3fe5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscammed-internet-provider-lower-my-bill-deepfakes-ai-2025-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Customers%20are%20turning%20the%20tables%20on%20call%20centers%20with%20their%20own%20robot%20voices.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ahoover%40insider.com%20(Amanda%20Hoover)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscammed-internet-provider-lower-my-bill-deepfakes-ai-2025-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22For%20Delhi%20Blast%2C%20Mobiles%20Bought%20From%20Nepal%2C%20SIMs%20From%20Kanpur%2C%20Say%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22Seven%20second-hand%20mobile%20phones%20were%20bought%20from%20Nepal%20for%20the%20operation%2C%20say%20sources.%20Also%2C%2017%20SIM%20cards%20were%20used%2C%20out%20of%20which%20six%20were%20bought%20in%20Kanpur.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1763370493000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-11%2Frqn7llso_delhi-blast_625x300_17_November_25.jpeg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D120