t%20gains%20to%20too%20many%20participants%20in%20the%20AI%20supply%20chain%2C%20%26quot%3Bthey%20may%20imply%20excessive%20aggregate%20revenue%20and%20profit%20gains.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20risk%2C%20according%20to%20Goldman's%20analysts%2C%20is%20assuming%20early%20profits%20will%20last.%20Productivity%20gains%20can%20boost%20earnings%20at%20first%2C%20but%20competition%20and%20new%20investment%20usually%20eat%20into%20those%20returns%20over%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoldman's%20report%20came%20amid%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-ai-bubble-crash-outlook-forecast-debate-valuation-risk-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eintense%20debate%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20whether%20the%20AI-fueled%20rally%20is%20in%20bubble%20territory%20as%20major%20US%20indexes%20breached%20record%20highs%20relentlessly%20this%20year%20before%20coming%20off%20sharply%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228b769315-d8a3-4759-ad68-82da6812813f%5C%22%3EThe%20macro%20AI%20math%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Goldman%20Sachs%20analysts%20estimate%20AI%20could%20bring%20roughly%20%248%20trillion%20in%20extra%20revenue%20to%20US%20companies%2C%20though%20the%20final%20haul%20could%20land%20anywhere%20between%20%245%20trillion%20and%20%2419%20trillion.%20The%20analysts%20did%20not%20put%20a%20time%20period%20on%20these%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20benefits%20are%20enough%20to%20justify%20current%20and%20anticipated%20levels%20of%20investment%20spending%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20note%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20added%20that%20the%20value%20of%20AI-related%20companies%20has%20risen%20by%20over%20%2419%20trillion%20since%20the%20introduction%20of%20ChatGPT%20%E2%80%94%20suggesting%20the%20market%20may%20have%20already%20priced%20in%20much%20of%20AI's%20potential%20upside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20added%20that%20while%20markets%20should%20price%20in%20gains%20from%20AI%20ahead%20of%20time%20if%20they%20expect%20them%2C%20the%20current%20valuation%20picture%20is%20%26quot%3Bfurther%20advanced%20than%20the%20macro%20story.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20risk%2C%20they%20added%2C%20is%20that%20while%20high%20valuations%20can%20hold%20up%20when%20the%20economy%20is%20strong%2C%20investors%20often%20end%20up%20paying%20the%20price%20when%20growth%20slows%20or%20the%20cycle%20turns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20Goldman%20analysts%20stopped%20short%20of%20calling%20the%20rally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-bubble-boom-goldman-sachs-crash-risk-forecast-outlook-valuation-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20bubble.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20add%20that%20markets%20often%20price%20in%20future%20gains%20early%20%E2%80%94%20and%20even%20after%20such%20big%20rallies%2C%20valuations%20could%20keep%20rising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20long%20as%20both%20the%20economy%20and%20the%20AI%20investment%20boom%20remain%20on%20track%2C%20we%20think%20markets%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20continue%20to%20take%20a%20more%20optimistic%20view%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMarkets%20remain%20on%20edge%20over%20sky-high%20tech%20valuations%20as%20investors%20weigh%20whether%20massive%20AI%20investments%20will%20deliver%20real%20returns%20%E2%80%94%20or%20repeat%20past%20bubbles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20JPMorgan%20warned%20that%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-stocks-market-outlook-dot-com-bubble-prediction-jpmorgan-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebiggest%20fear%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20red-hot%20AI%20trade%20is%20that%20it%20could%20mirror%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-bubble-nasdaq-correction-ai-2000-dot-com-bubble-crash-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edot-com%20boom%20and%20bust%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20late%201990s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20were%20relatively%20large%20sums%20of%20money%20being%20spent%20without%20a%20clear%20und