enging%20conditions%20for%20the%20latter.%20These%20ground%20vehicles%20come%20in%20many%20shapes%20and%20sizes%20and%20are%20often%20deployed%20to%20perform%20tasks%20that%20infantry%20might%20otherwise%20have%20to%20undertake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20poor%20visibility%20from%20heavy%20fog%20has%20long%20been%20a%20major%20concern%20for%20pilots%20flying%20drones%20in%20combat%2C%20with%20Ukrainian%20troops%20regularly%20telling%20Business%20Insider%20that%20no%20reliable%20solution%20for%20bad%20weather%20has%20been%20found%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFog%20is%20fog%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20drone%20pilot%20with%20the%20Flying%20Skulls%20battalion%20on%20Wednesday.%20Their%20identity%20is%20known%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrone%20pilots%20and%20makers%20have%20often%20advocated%20for%20consistent%20artillery%20fire%20to%20prevent%20Russia%20from%20advancing%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20weather%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%2C%20in%20recent%20days%2C%20used%20the%20cover%20of%20heavy%20fog%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-drones-heavy-fog-russia-advance-pokrovsk-motorbikes-cars-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epress%20deeper%20into%20Pokrovsk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20Ukrainian%20units%20reporting%20a%20surge%20in%20troops%20attempting%20to%20push%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20has%20said%20that%20his%20troops%20there%20are%20likely%20outnumbered%20eight%20to%20one.%20On%20Tuesday%2C%20he%20warned%20that%20Russia%20has%20markedly%20ramped%20up%20the%20intensity%20of%20assaults%20in%20the%20key%20city%2C%20which%20serves%20as%20a%20transport%20hub%20for%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20situation%20there%20is%20difficult%2C%20and%20in%20particular%20due%20to%20weather%20conditions%20that%20favor%20attacks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Telegram.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20has%20lately%20seen%20Russia%20relyin